  <brief_title>A Phase III Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of Satavaptan Versus Placebo in Patients With Dilutional Hyponatremia</brief_title>
  <acronym>AQUARIST1</acronym>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Multicenter Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of Two Doses of Satavaptan (SR121463B) Versus Placebo in Patients With Dilutional Hyponatremia Due to the Syndrome of Inappropriate Antidiuretic Hormone Secretion (SIADH)</official_title>
