  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to assess the efficacy of satavaptan versus placebo in
      participants with dilutional hyponatremia due to SIADH.

      Secondary objectives are to assess the safety of satavaptan, the maintenance of effect, and
      the clinical benefit in these participants.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
